  <h2>The Bottom Line</h2>
  <p>There's no single right answer for every inherited property situation. If the house is in great shape and you have time, listing with a Realtor might net you more. If you're dealing with out-of-state logistics, difficult condition, multiple heirs, or just want it resolved cleanly — a cash sale is often the smartest and simplest path forward.</p>
